# expense-analyzer
⇒ The Smart Expense Analyzer is a Python-based project that includes the analysis and processing of daily expenses. The project organizes the unstructured data, calculates category-wise expenses, and offers overall insights.

🚀 Features
⇒ Categorize the expenses (Food, Travel, Shopping, etc.)
⇒ Calculate the total expenses for each category
⇒ Calculate the overall expenses

🧠 Concepts Used
⇒ Dictionaries (Grouping Data)
⇒ Lists (Store Multiple Values)
⇒ Loops (Process Data)
⇒ Conditional Statements (Build Logic)

💻 Tech Stack
⇒Python

